  "prompt": "Which are the good CA coaching centres in south Delhi?",
  "response": "South Delhi is known for having some of the best CA coaching centers in India. Here are some of the reputed ones:\n\n### 1. **Ednovate (EduPristine)**  \n   - **Location:** Kalkaji, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Offers structured CA Foundation, Intermediate, and Final coaching programs. Known for experienced faculty and comprehensive study material.  \n   - **Contact:** Check their website for details.\n\n### 2. **Study At Home (SAH) Classes**  \n   - **Location:** Near PVR Priya, Vasant Vihar, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Known for personalized attention and small batch sizes. Offers classes for CA Foundation, Intermediate, and Final levels.  \n   - **Contact:** Visit their website or phone for details.\n\n### 3. **Pace Commerce**  \n   - **Location:** Near Lajpat Nagar Metro, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Renowned for CA Foundation and Intermediate coaching. Focuses on conceptual clarity and regular mock tests.  \n   - **Contact:** Check their website for exact locations and contact info.\n\n### 4. **J. K. Shah Classes**  \n   - **Location:** Kalkaji, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** One of the oldest and most respected CA coaching centers. Offers classes for all three levels of CA with experienced faculty.  \n   - **Contact:** Visit their official website for details.\n\n### 5. **Mentor Education**  \n   - **Location:** Mehrauli, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Known for its structured curriculum and regular test series. Offers offline and online classes for CA aspirants.  \n   - **Contact:** Check their website for more information.\n\n### 6. **CAG EduTech**  \n   - **Location:** Kalkaji, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Provides comprehensive CA coaching with a focus on practical learning and doubt-solving sessions.  \n   - **Contact:** Visit their website for details.\n\n### 7. **Genesis Classes**  \n   - **Location:** South Extension, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Known for its experienced faculty and interactive teaching methods. Offers classes for all CA levels.  \n   - **Contact:** Check their website or contact their office.\n\n### 8. **BRM Group of Institutions (BRM Classes)**  \n   - **Location:** Lajpat Nagar, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Focuses on CA Foundation and Intermediate with a strong emphasis on problem-solving and conceptual understanding.  \n   - **Contact:** Visit their website for more details.\n\n### 9. **AKP Classes**  \n   - **Location:** Near Kalkaji Mandir, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Known for its dedicated faculty and regular test series. Offers coaching for all levels of CA.  \n   - **Contact:** Check their website or visit their office.\n\n### 10. **Gag Classes**  \n   - **Location:** Near Greater Kailash, South Delhi  \n   - **Highlights:** Provides personalized coaching for CA aspirants with a focus on exam-oriented preparation.  \n   - **Contact:** Visit their website for details.\n\n### Tips for Choosing the Right Coaching Center:  \n- **Faculty:** Check the experience and reputation of the faculty.  \n- **Batch Size:** Smaller batches ensure personalized attention.  \n- **Study Material:** Quality of study material and test series is crucial.  \n- **Reviews:** Read reviews or talk to past students for feedback.  \n- **Location:** Choose a center that is easily accessible.  \n\nBefore enrolling, visit the centers, attend demo classes, and evaluate their teaching methods and infrastructure.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
